The following components were adapted from the original InfiniteRadio project:
- WebRTC streaming architecture and Opus encoding configuration
- Smoothstep crossfade algorithm for audio transitions
- Web UI design patterns (dark mode, genre selection)

The original InfiniteRadio source code is preserved in the _original/ directory
for reference and attribution purposes.
